
Usage: leshif-wol [-OPTION] [VALUE] [-OPTION] [VALUE] ...
       leshif-wol - m [hardware_address] -i [ip_address] -p [port]

Options:
    -h --help displays leshif-wol usage information
    -v  displays leshif-wol version
    -m  sets hardware_address (required option)
    -i  sets destination IP address. Default address: net-interface broadcast address
    -p  sets destination port. Default port: 9
    -n  sets used network interface
    -f  full sending mod (used all net-interfaces)
    -na displays all network interface
    -nu displays used network interface

